race.comment: IMMORTAL STAR (2) is neither immortal or a star but she is fit, in form, and in the right race. Much too good here before going to Sale and scrambling in against a similar looking line up. TANGO JEWEL (5) was among those beaten by her there. Not a lot to find to turn the tables and certainly wary of that. MYSTIC REIGN (7) isn't quite at her best this prep but she hasn't been bad enough to rule a line just yet. PERILOUS FIGHTER (3) gets a nice weight drop from a last start fourth at Sale. JAKIVY (9) has commenced his campaign with three solid runs, the latest at Pakenham. Should be hard fit fourth up.
